{"tid":754814,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"官宣了也要搶！曝巴塞4100萬歐簽巴西妖鋒達協議","createTime":"2018-07-24T16:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T08:42:48.000Z","uid":147522,"like":11,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"687f2dfa4823f0d918c665a9b1110b5c43bdcd5a","tid":754814,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:50:16.000Z","msg":"　　波爾多的巴西翼鋒馬高姆的轉會出現了戲劇性的劇情，在羅馬和波爾多官方確認就馬高姆轉會達成協議後，巴塞突然加入了轉會中，為馬高姆開出了報價，致使波爾多推遲了轉會的進行，現在情況有了新的進展。<br />\n<br />\n　　據西班牙媒體RAC1報導，巴塞已經就馬高姆的轉會和波爾多達成協議，球員將在當地時間今天下午飛往巴塞隆拿。據悉，巴塞開出的報價為4100萬歐元，之前羅馬的報價為4000萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n　　之前，巴塞曾經向車路士報價威廉，但他們開出的5500萬英鎊再一次遭到了車路士的拒絕，因此巴塞選擇轉攻馬高姆。據著名轉會專家迪馬斯奧報導，羅馬還在努力說服馬高姆，希望他能履行承諾。<br />\n<br />\n　　21歲的馬高姆上季在法甲出場35次攻入12球並有7次助攻，表現不俗。"},{"pid":"e26ac0c1c4fee5ede4bfb7009dd8a9ab9012c12d","tid":754814,"uid":69213,"like":16,"dislike":36,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:57:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25ef468c64e3fe58bc553f028a8c9bbfc0202784","tid":754814,"uid":5649,"like":68,"dislike":18,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:58:48.000Z","msg":"賤種疤狗"},{"pid":"4f7d67bf0b13b3738cd334e034aeb1d538cfaa5a","tid":754814,"uid":23815,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:59:45.000Z","msg":"40m+1啲朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbfb4a5ee5f480ad78c3314273050bcfe035c80","tid":754814,"uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4f7d67bf0b13b3738cd334e034aeb1d538cfaa5a","tid":754814,"uid":23815,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:59:45.000Z","msg":"40m+1啲朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:10:31.000Z","msg":"學雲爺爺"},{"pid":"ab0